<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>MacMenuBar.com (中文)</title><link>https://macmenubar.com</link><description>精心整理的1300多款Mac菜单栏应用目录</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 14:40:27 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>Raybeam</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/raybeam/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/raybeam.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Raybeam" height="350" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/raybeam.webp" width="400"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Raybeam 让你在视频通话中共享屏幕的一个可拖动、可调整大小的部分，从而轻松只展示重要内容，避免将整个桌面暴露给同事，防止意外混乱。&lt;/p&gt;
